            "body": "Hi @justinmk \nI dug through the code base to understand this issue better and found the following details:\nWe need to modify the data being pass to the `AutoPatCmd_S` struct defined [here](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/903335a6d50b020b36d1c4d5e9da362c31439d6e/src/nvim/autocmd_defs.h#L50C1-L50C8)\nWe could pass this while constructing the struct [here](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/903335a6d50b020b36d1c4d5e9da362c31439d6e/src/nvim/autocmd.c#L1847) ensuring we include `file`, `match` and `buf` information.\n\nPlease correct me if I am wrong, also tell me which files lua side changes will be required?",
